<h1>{$node_name}</h1>

<p>
	Integration Server (IS) is powerful application server that extends Elastix dial plan functionality and Visual Dialplan. 
</p>

<br/>

<p>
	It is specially designed to simplify working with third party servers (database servers, email servers etc.) and services from within the Elastix dial plan.  
</p>

<p>
	Integration Server comes with support for Visual Dialplan building blocks that provide intuitive interface to easily access those third party servers and service, like execute SQL queries on a remote database server (MS SQL, MySQL, Postgres etc.), send emails and more, directly from within the dial plan.
</p>

<p>
	It also extends Visual Dialplan with fully featured SQL query editor and email editor.
</p>

